summary: Prof: “Do you you still honestly hold that belief? As I tried to tell you 10 years ago I had-”” Prof: “MMMPH?!?” Skitt: “Gael...
body:
Prof: “Do you you still honestly hold that belief? As I tried to tell you 10 years ago I had-””

Prof: “MMMPH?!?”

Skitt: “Gael STOP!! She was about to say some-”

Gael: “I don’t care what she was gonna say…I don’t care! I’m TIRED OF BEING AFRAID OF FACING THE PAST! I’M TIRED OF IT!”

Gael: “I’M GONNA FACE IT HEAD ON…AND DESTROY MY PROBLEMS AT THE SOURCE!”

Gael: “I’ve been holding on to this for years.”

Gael: “I will finally get revenge for him.”

blog.name: weirdandwackypokefusions
blog.title: Well that's strange!
blog.description:
Welcome!  I create, using the all-mighty classic Microsoft XP Paint, my own pokemon fusions. All the sprites come from pokestadium and usually people on deviantart/ the xy/sun&moon sprite project. I don't own any of the sprite used, I just fuse them! 
REQUESTS ARE OPEN! Ask Box: 3/15.
PLEASE FEEL FREE TO DRAW MY FUSIONS!!  I absolutely love it when people draw them! There's no need to ask either! Just make sure you tag me so them I can see it!
I hope you enjoy my fusions!

summary: Diaymin Diancie and Shaymin Sky Form Fusion Rock/Flying Type Ability: Overcoat Stats: HP - 75, Atk - 105, Def - 125, SpA - 130,...
caption:
Diaymin

Diancie and Shaymin Sky Form Fusion

Rock/Flying Type

Ability: Overcoat

Stats: HP - 75, Atk - 105, Def - 125, SpA - 130, SpD - 125, Spe - 120

The Floating Rock Pokemon

Diaymin has crystal growing out of it and they constantly grow.  It hasn’t learnt how to walk as it has such weak legs so it found a rock, sat on top of it and embedded levitating powers into it to move around. It glides around on its rock and will challenge pokemon to races. 

Request for anon. I hope you like it! You didn’t specify which shaymin you wanted me to fuse so I decided to fuse sky form.

summary: DAY 9 of the Pokémon marathon on Twitch is now LIVE! The next 15 episodes that is going to be streamed (from Season 2) will...
body:
DAY 9 of the Pokémon marathon on Twitch is now LIVE!

The next 15 episodes that is going to be streamed (from Season 2) will feature the remaining episodes left for the Orange Islands arc! These include the 2 final Orange Crew gym battles, the episode where Charizard FINALLY becomes obedient, the full league battle between Ash and supreme gym leader Drake, and the return of Brock! All in this final rotation of the week :D

The episode set will show 3 times just so you won’t miss the stream depending on your schedule: 10am | 4:50pm | 11:30pm (PDT, UTC−07:00)

Watching with Twitch chat could be the best (or worst) experience you’ll ever have! But if you want a more comfy chat experience, feel free to talk/chat about the marathon in my Pokémon Discord server PokéTōku —> Invite link here :)
